      <title>戴蒙表示怀疑通胀能否回到美联储 2% 的目标水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/dimon-says-he-s-skeptical-inflation-gets-back-to-fed-s-2-target</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通首席执行官杰米戴蒙表示，他对通胀率能否回到美联储 2% 的目标表示怀疑，并指出存在赤字支出和“世界再军事化”等风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/dimon-says-he-s-skeptical-inflation-gets-back-to-fed-s-2-target</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 18:19:14 GMT</pubDate>
